data.description: This very nice three-bedroom, two-bath home with attached two-car garage on four lots is located on a quiet paved street just minutes from access to Lake LBJ. Open concept living, split floor plan gives everyone space and privacy, kitchen with breakfast bar overlooks family room that features corner stone fireplace. The exterior features a fully privacy fenced back yard and back gate with a 936-square-foot workshop (three car parking) and separate storage building.  There is plenty of room for added improvements in the future. Enjoy easy access to constant level Lake LBJ just down the street through several city owned waterfront parks.
